| t.config().capabilities.contains(crate::target::TargetCapabilities::FETCH))\n        .cloned()\n        .collect();\n\n    if fetchable.is_empty() {\n        return Err(TransportError::Network(\"No fetchable targets available\".to_string()));\n    }\n\n    // ... rest uses fetchable instead of targets\n```\n\nAlso update `quorum_target_count()` and `quorum_target_ids()` in `coordinator.rs` to use `TargetCapabilities::QUORUM_CREDIT` instead of `TargetKind::Stable`:\n\n```rust\n// Instead of: pool.targets_by_kind(TargetKind::Stable)\n// Use: pool.all_targets().iter().filter(|t| t.config().capabilities.contains(TargetCapabilities::QUORUM_CREDIT))\n```\n\nAdd tests for capability filtering.\n\n## Existing Code Context\n\n`TransportCoordinator` struct (coordinator.rs):\n- Has `http_pool: Option<Arc<TransportPool<HttpTarget>>>` and optional mqtt_pool\n- Already has `set_http_pool()`, `subscribe()`, `submit_tiered()` methods\n- `quorum_target_count()` and `quorum_target_ids()` currently filter by `TargetKind::Stable`\n\n`TransportPool<T>` (pool.rs):\n- Has `add_target()`, `remove_target()`, `all_targets()`, `healthy_targets()`, `targets_by_kind()`\n- `fetch_from_targets()` fetches from all passed targets — needs FETCH capability filter\n\n`TargetCapabilities` (target.rs):\n- `SEND`, `FETCH`, `QUORUM_CREDIT`, `REPLICATE` flags\n- Stable defaults: `SEND | FETCH | QUORUM_CREDIT`\n- Ephemeral defaults: `SEND` only\n\n`TargetConfig`:\n- Has `capabilities: TargetCapabilities` field\n- Has `kind: TargetKind` field\n\n## Branch Setup\n\nWork from `feat/target-capabilities` branch. Create a new branch:\n```bash\ngit switch feat/target-capabilities\ngit switch -c feat/coordinator-mutations-and-fetch-filter\n```\n\n## After Implementation\n\n1. Run `cargo test -p reme-transport` and `cargo clippy -p reme-transport --all-features -- -D warnings` and `cargo fmt --all -- --check`\n2. Invoke the `simplify` skill to review and clean up your changes\n3. Commit with a clear message (can b